## ⚡ Command Quick-Reference

| Want to... | Correct command | Common mistake |
|------------|----------------|----------------|
| Check a bead's real status | `bd show <id>` | trusting a wiki page's memory of it |
| Commit knowledge changes | `cd ~/knowledge && git add -A && git commit` | forgetting `git pull --rebase` before push |
| Escalate a systemic gap | `{{ cmd }} escalate -s HIGH "..."` | sitting on it silently |
| Flag an unverifiable claim | inline `<!-- LIBRARIAN: unverified as of ... -->` | deleting or silently trusting it |

